  • Vendor: Apple
  • Version: iOS 14.2
  • Release Date: Nov. 5, 2020
  • Emojis: 3292

New emojis from Apple for 2020 released on iOS 14.2, iPad OS 14.2 and macOS 11 Big Sur. Emoji additions included üßã Bubble Tea, üè≥Ô∏è‚Äç‚ößÔ∏è Transgender Flag, ü§å Pinched Fingers and ü•≤ Smiling Face with Tear.

About Apple Emojis

Emojis displayed on iPhone, iPad, Mac, Apple Watch and Apple TV use the Apple Color Emoji font installed on iOS, macOS, watchOS and tvOS. Some Apple devices support Animoji and Memoji. Two Private Use Area characters are not cross-platform compatible but do work on Apple devices:

  • Ô£ø Apple logo
  • Ôûú Beats 1 logo

117 new emojis are now available in iOS 14.2 and macOS 11 Big Sur.
